	<body>
        <div class="topGradient"></div>
        <span style="font-weight:bold; font-size:22px;">Help/FAQ</span>
        <dl>
            <dt>How do I play actions cards?</dt>
            <dd>
                Just click on the action card you want to play.
            </dd>
            <dt>How do I play treasure cards?</dt>
            <dd>
                There is a "Play Treasure Cards" link above the cards in your hand when it is your turn.
                <br>
                Clicking this link will play all of the treasure cards that do not depend on the order they are played in.
                <br>
                All treasure cards can be played by clicking the card you want to play.
            </dd>
            <dt>Shortcut Keys</dt>
            <dd>
                t - Play All Treasure Cards
            </dd>
            <dd>
                e - End Turn
            </dd>
            <dt>Chat Commands</dt>
            <dd>
                /lobby &lt;message&gt; Send a message to everyone in the lobby
            </dd>
            <dd>
                /whisper or /w &lt;player&gt; &lt;message&gt; Send a private message to a player
            </dd>
            <dt>Questions, Comments, Bugs</dt>
            <dd>
                Send an email to <a href="mailto:icesphere12@gmail.com">icesphere12@gmail.com</a>
            </dd>
